{
  "texts": [
    "Our task then is to predict the target word in a masked conversation, i.e., target word prediction (TWP).",
    "TWP represents a simplified version of next-word generation utilised by decoder models.",
    "Since decoder models are adept in tasks involving causal language modeling, TWP is a reasonable task choice.",
    "Upon observing that the TWP performances for en-IN and en-NG are lower than those of en-US, the objective of LORDD is to improve the TWP performances for en-IN and en-NG.",
    "LORDD employs a combination of two LoRA-based (Hu et al., 2022) adapters."
  ]
}